src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5826576de86a0b31b53c6849053993946957ac9","tid":390374,"uid":109557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T10:07:12.000Z","msg":"依家個啲奧義下下都好似爆咗個原子彈咁   但係又扣得雞水咁多血  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c25ca1ebd78978dedce39bbed6248e9460245bb4","tid":390374,"uid":82889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T10:14:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個陣放學成日上fd屋企打<br />\n禁到個L2 R2制壞晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n日日係到練d角色體術駁忍術/大技combo<br />\n<br />\n利伸：真係冇玩過ps3 火影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都經歷過果個年代<br />\n但呢個完全係童年回憶加持先覺得咁正<br />\n新果代無論故事關卡定打交都平衡好多"},{"pid":"db08d30e30cfcaface439e689eb9138b392f09cc","tid":390374,"uid":2196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T10:14:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好唔好玩就見人見智，但我最記得Ps2鼬開月讀好屈同埋出超必既時候雙方要狂禁掣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n鼬打npc淨係屈豪火球<br />\n同人打就屈白魔鏡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個時用4代一開始狂禁左/右+O屈人 普攻快到ON9</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲有狗西鬼童丸"},{"pid":"a794e0faab4d40c7756885b38fc35b3d33b0c441","tid":390374,"uid":82889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T10:15:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新版玩法完全係消耗曬對面嘅替身次數再體術combo<br />\n只要唔係盲目用替身好少可中大招，普通招威力又低過體術combo</blockquote><br />\n舊版咪又係無限替身"},{"pid":"2c29fc8a1a4c66a609f2094b7c7697b1a2e3ba1e","tid":390374,"uid":82889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T10:16:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>舊版初代招樹界降誔<br />\n成分鐘咁長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最鐘意屈大技睇片</blockquote><br />\n格鬥驚黎講睇太長動畫其實壞事黎<br />\n不過舊版每個角色有三種大技真係好有心機<br />\n新版d製作費落左去整故事關卡"},{"pid":"aa9cbb5f0d8d1ab4ece82ddc441164e140e89daf","tid":390374,"uid":2196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T10:17:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>個陣放學成日上fd屋企打<br />\n禁到個L2 R2制壞晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n日日係到練d角色體術駁忍術/大技combo<br />\n<br />\n利伸：真係冇玩過ps3 火影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都經歷過果個年代<br />\n但呢個完全係童年回憶加持先覺得咁正<br />\n新果代無論故事關卡定打交都平衡好多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n小五六喪打ps2二三<br />\n之後到大學先痴人機玩左陣佐助打鼬劇情<br />\n對戰唔敢講；但劇力真係贏幾條街既"},{"pid":"02fa8c77de2706e0280a1b8d28f089dd84715149","tid":390374,"uid":2196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T10:18:35.000Z","msg":"講緊storm劇力"},{"pid":"32288f933dd5238ab6b3198d84519e3acebd4b12","tid":390374,"uid":82889,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T10:19:23.000Z","msg":"覺得舊版好玩d冇問題，但成日見到d老屎忽冇玩新版剩係話ps2最好玩就覺得好嘔心<br />\n新版火影同batman arkham系列並稱做最成功漫畫改篇遊戲<br />\n係班老屎忽口中講到一文不值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"404438b9b8c125dabe2b147c9463ca986d8a98c2","tid":390374,"uid":58945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T10:20:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>新版玩法完全係消耗曬對面嘅替身次數再體術combo<br />\n只要唔係盲目用替身好少可中大招，普通招威力又低過體術combo</blockquote><br />\n舊版咪又係無限替身</blockquote><br />\n冇氣就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出技,大絕,替身都靠氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />果時同frd玩,禁左用幫手,好正"},{"pid":"625635d24ac16cbf16e194acee1e36493677fbc2","tid":390374,"uid":82889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T10:20:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>個陣放學成日上fd屋企打<br />\n禁到個L2 R2制壞晒<img src=\"/a